<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="extend-v">extend <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'stend/    美 /ɪk'stend/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1vt">1.<strong>vt 伸开；展开；伸出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Extend</strong> your left <strong>hand</strong>.
把左手伸出来。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-vt-vi">2.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (使) 延伸；(使) 延长：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This road extends to the river.
这条路延伸到河边。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Their stay extends to the New Year.
他们要一直待到新年。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The travelers decided to extend their visit to see more about the beautiful country.
游客们决定延长逗留时间，多看看这个美丽的国家。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-vt-vi">3.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (使) 扩大；(使) 扩展：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>extended family</strong>
大家庭(几代同堂的家庭)</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company extended its services to Hong Kong.
该公司将其业务扩展到香港。</p></div>

<h4 id="4vt">4.<strong>vt[正式用语]提供；给予：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The chairman <strong>extended a</strong> warm <strong>welcome to</strong> the guest speaker.
主席向特邀演讲者表示热烈欢迎。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I would like to <strong>extend</strong> my <strong>thanks to</strong> all our teachers,parents and families,who have done so much for us over the years.
我要感谢这些年来为我们做了很多的老师、父母和家人们。</p><footer>北师大新必修①-3</footer></div></div>